123
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,679
to submit some documents to school.

124
00:11:36,169 --> 00:11:37,330
Thank you.

125
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:53,379
Your food is delicious.

126
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,529
Were you Eun Sang's classmate?

127
00:12:08,429 --> 00:12:10,399
Are you close to her?

128
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,120
I have a crush on Eun Sang.

129
00:12:38,759 --> 00:12:43,730
I see that you've moved
to a beautiful town by the ocean.

130
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,370
And you met Tan there.

131
00:12:49,610 --> 00:12:51,039
That wasn't on purpose.

132
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:54,809
This is why I wanted to send you
to the other side of the world.

133
00:12:56,179 --> 00:12:58,919
When you broke the promise
you made with me and ran away,

134
00:12:59,279 --> 00:13:01,549
I thought you got the message.

135
00:13:01,889 --> 00:13:03,919
I trusted you and let you be.

136
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:05,220
But...

137
00:13:05,990 --> 00:13:10,029
