and tell me that you met Tan?

138
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,429
- Tan is...
- How dare you say his name?

139
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:15,929
kind,

140
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,169
honest,

141
00:13:19,269 --> 00:13:20,769
and compassionate.

142
00:13:22,269 --> 00:13:23,309
That is why...

143
00:13:24,610 --> 00:13:26,110
I really liked him.

144
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:28,009
How can you say such a thing?

145
00:13:28,110 --> 00:13:30,649
Because I'm not at fault
for catching feelings for him.

146
00:13:30,649 --> 00:13:33,549
No, it is your fault
when you've been paid with my money,

147
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:36,190
benefitted from me,
and yet, grew feelings for him.

148
00:13:36,289 --> 00:13:39,460
I will make sure to pay back
what you've paid on our behalf.

149
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:42,789
But since you paid our debt
without asking my family,

150
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:47,399
I will also diligently pay you back
in my own ways.

151
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:49,429
Are you saying...

152
00:13:50,269 --> 00:13:53,100
that you'll date him again
once you pay me back?

153
00:13:55,110 --> 00:13:57,639
How can you young kid
be so fearless?

154
00:13:57,740 --> 00:13:58,740
Because...

155
00:13:59,909 --> 00:14:01,210
I like Tan.

156
00:14:03,149 --> 00:14:05,620
I still like Tan.

157
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,919
Even if you keep scaring me,

158
00:14:09,389 --> 00:14:10,690
and even if I'm terrified,

159
00:14:12,289 --> 00:14:14,690
I can't lie to you that I no longer
have feelings for him.

160
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,230
However,

161
00:14:18,299 --> 00:14:21,100
I won't see him since you told me
not to.

162
00:14:23,899 --> 00:14:25,500
So, please,

163
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,840
