177
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,920
How dare an Info Desk employee...

178
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:17,750
come up all the way
to the Chairman's Office?

179
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,559
Such lowly trait wouldn't go
anywhere.

180
00:20:20,759 --> 00:20:23,589
How could you say such a thing?

181
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,160
Why not?

182
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:28,930
You and Tan both are too spoiled.

183
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:32,269
You're all living a life
that most people dream of,

184
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:35,240
yet you're all so greedy
to have everything you want.

185
00:20:36,369 --> 00:20:37,710
You told me to come.

186
00:20:39,009 --> 00:20:41,849
You were the one who told me
that I could come.

187
00:20:43,009 --> 00:20:45,920
You told me
that your office was at the top!

188
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:49,019
That's why my life is a mess
right now.

189
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:52,359
The household has become
so lowly...

190
00:20:52,589 --> 00:20:54,690
