by something cheap and shiny.

191
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:58,529
- Chairman Kim!
- Tell Tan.

192
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:01,329
When he doesn't know what to choose,

193
00:21:01,470 --> 00:21:03,700
