243
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:58,970
I won't get in your way.

244
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,470
I'll grant your wish.

245
00:25:02,670 --> 00:25:03,970
You can keep going up.

246
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:07,410
