as we walked through the crowd."

250
00:25:30,670 --> 00:25:33,500
"The bones and the muscles..."

251
00:25:33,740 --> 00:25:36,170
"that were desperately holding
onto each other."

252
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:39,309
"That's all I know about love."

253
00:25:41,039 --> 00:25:43,509
